      "comment": "WE LOVE CHARLIE (6) went back-to-back to begin this campaign, winning by 0.3L most recently and stretches to 1100m now. Riordan's 1.5kg claim comes in handy and she looks a progressive type on the rise. Needs a touch of luck from the draw but can continue her winning ways. SNEAKY SESSION (5) is another looking for the hat-trick, winning her past two at Geraldton, the latest by 0.6L. Tsang makes the trip with her and a better draw this time around is a big tick. Can extend her winning run. PERFECT SISTER (2) started this preparation with a win two runs ago. Couldn't follow that up last time out when sixth over 1100m at this track, beaten 3 lengths after being in the firing line on the corner. Looks well placed so expect a better run this time. MISS ROMPIN (7) was safely held when third last time out over 1240m at this track, beaten 3.5 lengths, after a win at this track at the previous outing. One of the main hopes. REGGIO CALABRIA (1) has to be included on recent form.",
